		introduction_tw = '雷丘，電屬性的鼠寶可夢。皮卡丘的進化型。其電擊超過十萬伏特，連印度象被電到都會暈倒。',
		introduction_en = 'Raichu, a Mouse Pokémon of the Electric element. Raichu is the evolved form of Pikachu. Its electric charges can reach even 100,000 volts. Careless contact can cause even an Indian elephant to faint.',
		introduction_vn = 'Raichu, a Mouse Pokémon of the Electric element. Raichu is the evolved form of Pikachu. Its electric charges can reach even 100,000 volts. Careless contact can cause even an Indian elephant to faint.',
		introduction_kr = '라이츄, 전기 타입의 쥐 포켓몬, 피카츄의 진화 형태, 전격이 10만 볼트를 넘을 때도 있으며, 인도코끼리조차 기절시킬 수 있다.',
		introduction_pt = 'Raichu, um Pokémon Rato do elemento Elétrico. Raichu é a forma evoluída de Pikachu. Suas cargas elétricas podem atingir até 100.000 volts. Contato descuidado pode fazer até mesmo um elefante indiano desmaiar.',
		introduction_th = 'ไรชู โปเกมอนหนูแห่งธาตุไฟฟ้า ไรชูคือร่างที่พัฒนาแล้วของปิกาจู ประจุไฟฟ้าของมันมีพลังถึง 100,000 โวลต์ การสัมผัสโดยประมาทอาจทำให้ช้างอินเดียหมดสติได้',
