		-- {2311, 2312, 2313}
		introduction = '猴怪，猪猴宝可梦。属于格斗类型，出拳神速，步伐轻盈。猴怪平时个性温和，但一旦激怒就会一发不可收拾。',
		introduction_tw = '猴怪，豬猴寶可夢。屬於格鬥類型，出拳神速，步伐輕盈。猴怪平時個性溫和，但一旦激怒就會一發不可收拾。',
		introduction_en = 'Mankey, a Pig Monkey Pokémon of the Fighting-type. Known for its superior footwork, it packs a powerful punch. Although Mankey is usually calm, it does have a bad temper. Once Mankey begins to Thrash, stopping it is impossible.',
		introduction_vn = 'Mankey, a Pig Monkey Pokémon of the Fighting-type. Known for its superior footwork, it packs a powerful punch. Although Mankey is usually calm, it does have a bad temper. Once Mankey begins to Thrash, stopping it is impossible.',
		introduction_kr = '망키, 돈숭이 포켓몬, 격투 타입으로, 주먹과 스텝이 매우 빠르다. 평소에는 온순하지만 화가 나면 걷잡을 수 없다.',
		introduction_pt = 'Mankey, um Pokémon Macaco-Porco do tipo Lutador. Conhecido por seu trabalho de pés superior, ele dá um soco poderoso. Embora Mankey geralmente seja calmo, ele tem um temperamento ruim. Uma vez que Mankey começa a Thrash, pará-lo é impossível.',
		introduction_th = 'มังกี้ โปเกมอนประเภทต่อสู้ มีลักษณะเด่นคือมีการเคลื่อนไหวเท้าที่ยอดเยี่ยม มีพลังโจมตีที่รุนแรง มังกี้มักจะใจเย็น แต่ก็มีนิสัยฉุนเฉียว เมื่อมังกี้เริ่มโจมตี จะไม่สามารถหยุดมันได้',
