		introduction_en = 'The Coconut Tree is a coconut Pokémon, and is also known as the walking rainforest. Each fruit has a face and its own will. Its special skill is hypnosis.',
		introduction_vn = 'The Coconut Tree is a coconut Pokémon, and is also known as the walking rainforest. Each fruit has a face and its own will. Its special skill is hypnosis.',
		introduction_kr = '코코넛 트리는 코코넛 포켓몬이며, 걷는 열대우림으로도 알려져 있습니다. 각 과일에는 얼굴과 의지가 있습니다. 특수 기술은 최면입니다.',
		introduction_pt = 'O Coconut Tree é um Pokémon coco, e também é conhecido como a floresta tropical ambulante. Cada fruta tem um rosto e sua própria vontade. Sua habilidade especial é a hipnose.',
		introduction_th = 'ต้นมะพร้าวเป็นโปเกมอนมะพร้าว และเป็นที่รู้จักในชื่อป่าฝนเดินได้ ผลไม้แต่ละชนิดมีใบหน้าและความตั้งใจเป็นของตัวเอง ความสามารถพิเศษของมันคือการสะกดจิต',
