		introduction_vn = 'Anything that looks edible, it will go on and swallow whole. Its stomach is tough enough to handle it even if the food has gone rotten.',
		introduction_kr = '일단 많이 먹고 보는 것에 푹 빠져 있다. 맛은 상관하지 않으며, 상했어도 신경 쓰지 않는다.',
		introduction_pt = 'Qualquer coisa que pareça comestível, ele vai engolir inteiro. Seu estômago é forte o suficiente para lidar com isso, mesmo que a comida tenha estragado.',
		introduction_th = 'อะไรก็ตามที่ดูน่ากินก็จะกลืนลงไปทั้งตัว ท้องของมันแข็งแกร่งพอที่จะรับมือได้แม้ว่าอาหารจะเน่าเสียแล้วก็ตาม',
