		introduction_en = 'Manaphy is a Water-type Mythical Pokémon. Although it is a Mythical Pokémon, Manaphy can lay eggs, and the Pokémon that hatches from them is Phione. Manaphy uses its innate mystical powers to communicate telepathically with any Pokémon.',
